OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWater chiefs' bonuses to be
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fblocked over pollution     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Executives at water companies could    
OL,6, lose their bonuses in future if the    
OL,7, firm they run causes environmental     
OL,8, damage, like letting illegal sewage    
OL,9, spills pollute a beach or river.       
OL,11,FEnvironment Secretary Stephen Barclay  
OL,12,Fsaid it was time water company bosses  
OL,13,F"took responsibility".                 
OL,15,FCampaigners and opposition parties said
OL,16,Fthey had been calling for restrictions 
OL,17,Fon water boss bonuses for some time.   
OL,19,FRegulator Ofwat will run a consultation
OL,20,Fon the proposal later this year.       
